data.description: Nestled along 80 feet of saltwater canal frontage, this home presents a unique opportunity for those seeking waterfront living.  A scenic 2-mile boat ride connects the property to the Intracoastal Waterway (ICW), offering convenient access to a broader water network. The residence features a screened pool with an outdoor shower, providing a relaxing space with spectacular views of the canal.  In addition, this residence comes equipped with a whole house generator, ensuring continuous functionality during hurricane seasons for added peace of mind.  Inside, the practical layout includes a large private office, ideal for those who work from home or need a dedicated workspace or a fourth bedroom.  The three bedrooms provide ample living space, while the primary bathroom stands out for its generous size.  Situated in proximity to shopping centers, restaurants, schools, and the beach, this home combines waterfront tranquility with easy access to essential amenities.  Additionally, European Village, a one-stop-destination for all things dining, shopping, and entertainment, is just down the road.  European Village boasts 7 eateries, multiple salons and boutique shops, 6 bars, and more, making it a convenient and vibrant hub for residents seeking diverse experiences.  Whether enjoying the scenic water views, exploring nearby conveniences, or indulging in the offerings of European Village, this property provides a balanced and comfortable lifestyle.  Roof 2018.  A/C 2023.
